Class AutoEncryptionSettings.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mongodb.AutoEncryptionSettings.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    AutoEncryptionSettings

    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class AutoEncryptionSettings.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    A builder for AutoEncryptionSettings so that AutoEncryptionSettings can be immutable, and to support easier construction through chaining.
